<<
InstallScript: <<
 install -d -m 755 %i/share/icons
 ( tar -cf - Crystal | ( cd %i/share/icons; tar -xf - ) )
<<
Description: Crystal icon set for KDE.
DescDetail: <<
Conectiva Crystal is a contemporary icon design used by default in the
Conectiva Linux distribution.
<<
DescPort: <<
NOTE: KDE packages do *not* have an -shlibs because of KDE's use of  
libltdl!  The .la's *must* be used in conjunction with the dynamic
libraries, and they are unversioned filenames, so multiple -shlibs would
conflict.
<<
